Package: rmetadata
Type: Package
Title: Work with many Scholarly Metadata APIs in R.
Description: A wrapper to get article metatdata from OAI-PMH servers, and
    other data sources, including Digital Public Library of America,
    HathiTrust, Europeana, and more.
